'''''Seasons of a Life,''''' ni filimi yasohotse 2010 nka [[Malawi]] Legal drama film iyoborwa na  Shemu Joyah na vyahinguwe n'Ivyabona FirstDawn Arts<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/ie/film832371.html</ref>.  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Bennie Msuku ayoboye hamwe na Neria Chikhosi, Flora Suya na Tapiwa Gwaza bagize uruhare runini<ref>https://www.kweli.tv/programs/seasons-of-a-life?locale=en</ref>.  

Ikinamico yemewe ninkiko yibanze kumukozi wo murugo wasambanijwe numukoresha we uharanira kwiha ku imbaraga no kuzamura imibereho ye<ref>https://africandiasporavideo.com/products/stories-of-motherhood-family-motel-seasons-of-a-life</ref>.  Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Göteborg muri [[Suwede]] ku ya 31 Mutarama 2010<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/ie/film832371.html</ref>. Iyi filime kandi yatorewe ibihembo mu birori bya [[Kenya]], Cairo, na Zanzibar<ref>https://intomalawi.wordpress.com/tag/seasons-of-a-life/</ref>.  Yatowe mu byiciro 8 mu bihembo bya 6 bya African Movie Academy Awards, harimo abahatanira ibihembo byiza byerekana amashusho meza hamwe n’umwimerere mwiza<ref>https://www.nyasatimes.com/malawian-film-wins-award-at-us-film-festival/</ref>. Umukinnyi wa filime, Tapiwa Gwaza yatsindiye igihembo cya Nollywood kubera ibikorwa byiza byakozwe numukinnyi ushyigikiwe<ref>https://kigalinews.wordpress.com/2010/05/08/tip-of-the-day-seasons-of-life-award-winning-real-african-movie/</ref>.

